---
// Footer.astro
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-slate-900 text-white mt-auto border-t border-slate-800">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
           <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Jour de <span class="text-teal-400">Chance</span></span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
          Nous transformons vos opportunités en succès grâce à une expertise digitale de pointe.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Navigation</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><a href="/" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Accueil</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Nos Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="/a-propos" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Qui sommes-nous ?</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Nous contacter</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <span>📧</span>
            <a href="mailto:contact@jourdechance.com" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">contact@jourdechance.com</a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-300">
            <span>📍</span>
            <span>Boulogne-Billancourt, 92100</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-300 text-xs">
             <span>🏢</span>
             <span>67 av. Pierre Grenier</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-slate-800 mt-12 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-xs text-slate-500">
      <p>&copy; $year Jour de Chance. Tous droits réservés.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-4 md:mt-0">
        <a href="/mentions-legales" class="hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors">Mentions Légales</a>
        <span class="text-slate-700">|</span>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors">Confidentialité</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
